title: iSkysoft Video Converter Ultimate 5.6.0.0 Multilingual
description:
******************************************************
iSkysoft Video Converter Ultimate 5.6.0.0 Multilingual
******************************************************

Convert Any Video and Audio Formats

- Convert HD Videos: Convert home videos from Camcorder in AVCHD, MTS, M2TS or other formats.

- Convert home Video Formats: Support all standard video formats such as WMV, MP4, MOV, FLV, MKV, AVI, etc.

- Convert home Audio Formats: Support regular audio formats like MP3, MKA, M4A, WAV, AC3, AAC, etc.

Supported Formats
-----------------

- Standard Videos: MP4, MOV(QuickTime), WMV, MKV, MTS, FLV, 3GP, AVI(XviD), MPG, MPEG1, MPEG2, M4V(without DRM), 3G2, TS, WebM, RM, RMVB, ASF, RMVB, OGV, VRO, TP, TRP, MXF, DivX, VOB, and more.
- HD Videos: HD MOV (MPEG-4, H.264), MOD (MPEG-2), HD WMV (VC-1), HD TOD (MPEG-2), HD MKV (H.264, MPEG-2), M2TS (AVCHD, H.264), MTS (AVCHD, H.264), HD TS, HD FLV, HD TRP, HD MPG, etc.
- Audio: MP3, WAV, AAC, M4A, MP2, AC3, NSV, AIFF, MKA, AMR, FLAC, APE, OGG, iPod Shuffle and Amazon Kindle.
- Online videos: YouTube, Vevo, Vimeo, Hulu,Dailymotion, AOL, Metacafe, BlipTV, FunnyOrDie, Break, Veoh, LiveLeak, VideoBash, eBaumsworld, MyVideo, 5min, GodTube, VideoJug, Nico Video, 100+ more and adult sites. 

More Features
-------------

- Merge Multiple Files: Allows you to merge multiple video clips into a single one. So that you can watch movie without pauses and gaps.
- Capture Screenshot: Comes with an in-app screenshot capturing program, and allow you share interesting moments of the video with your friends and family
- Full Utilization of Multi-core Processor: With a modern software design, you can tap into the full power of your computer's multi-core processor, and convert several video files at one go.
- Built-in Media Player: Directly play the converted videos to check the quality. Or even play your own desktop videos in any media formats.
- Record any Video: Automatically detected the video and record it with the "Record" button. Click the "Record" button again to stop recording and you get the recorded files.

System requirements: 32-bit/64-bit versions of Windows 2K / XP / Vista / 7 / 8 / 2003 / 10 / NT

Homepage http://www.iskysoft.us/video-converter-windows.html
